Grammar of graphics with ggplot2


ggplot2

  • most popular data visualization package for R

  • created by Hadley Wickham

  • implements Leland Wilkinson's Grammar of Graphics

  • built on the idea of adding layers

  • let's see how the layers work!



    • http://docs.ggplot2.org/current/
